{"tid":2081491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（一小時，兩單）寶林邨女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-06-27T09:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:12:43.000Z","uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e15e5313d4437af923b209a01d18b26c8eeb8d02","tid":2081491,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"將軍澳寶林邨寶智樓，下午1時11分，一名年約40歲女子，由中層單位墮下，跌在1樓簷篷。救援人員到場，經檢驗證實該女子不治。警方正調查死者身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n另外，下午2時許，一名16歲少女在將軍澳新都城2期的屋苑平台墮下，跌在6米下路面。救護員到場將少女送到伊利沙伯醫院治理，警方正調查事件。據悉，她受情緒病困擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200627/N5ECKAVPSSQZOTWUJNP5I6ZAMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200627%2FN5ECKAVPSSQZOTWUJNP5I6ZAMM%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=89ae33c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200627%2FN5ECKAVPSSQZOTWUJNP5I6ZAMM%2F&h=94eb843d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200627/N5ECKAVPSSQZOTWUJNP5I6ZAMM/</a>"},{"pid":"61eacca8dd1e2ad15cabad6fa0502ef95ed3b65e","tid":2081491,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}